WEBVTT

1
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:19.000
Pen pal

2
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.600
Peppa and her friends
are at their playgroup.

3
00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:22.500
Children.

4
00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:25.000
Who would like a pen pal?

5
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.600
Me! Me!

6
00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:29.100
What's a pen pal?

7
00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:34.083
A pen pal is a boy or girl
you can write letters to.

8
00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:37.100
This is a girl lives in France.

9
00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:40.200
Her name is Delphine donkey...

10
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:43.000
Can Delphine donkey be my pen pal?

11
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:44.600
Of course, Peppa.

12
00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:49.583
Hooray!

13
00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:51.100
It is early morning.

14
00:00:51.100 --> 00:00:55.200
Mr Zebra the postman is delivering
a letterto peppa's house.

15
00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:56.200
Post!

16
00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:59.400
Peppa and George love it
when the post arrives.

17
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:02.000
It's address to Ms. Peppa pig.

18
00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.700
That's me.

19
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:06.200
Mummy, can you read it for me?

20
00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:07.700
Of course.

21
00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:09.700
It's from Delphine donkey...

22
00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:12.000
My pen pal.

23
00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.500
What does she say?

24
00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:17.800
Bonjour, peppa, Comment sa va

25
00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:21.700
Mummy, why are you
saying those funny words?

26
00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:23.100
It's French, peppa.

27
00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:24.600
It means hello,

28
00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:25.800
how are you?

29
00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:27.300
What else does she say?

30
00:01:27.300 --> 00:01:29.400
Mm... I'll help.

31
00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:34.383
Jes les princess pet
avac memes ames...

32
00:01:35.900 --> 00:01:37.900
Clever daddy.

33
00:01:37.900 --> 00:01:40.700
I am an expert in French.

34
00:01:40.700 --> 00:01:42.100
What does it mean?

35
00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:44.100
Mm.

36
00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:49.083
Daddy pig clean his glasses so
he can see the letter more clearly.

37
00:01:49.500 --> 00:01:50.900
It's no good.

38
00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:52.400
It's nonsense.

39
00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:57.383
It means I like fairy princess
and playing with my friends.

40
00:01:57.800 --> 00:01:59.500
That's what I was going to say.

41
00:01:59.500 --> 00:02:01.500
Haha...

42
00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:03.800
I want to talk French.

43
00:02:03.800 --> 00:02:06.300
Maybe you could
talk to Delphine Donkey...

44
00:02:06.300 --> 00:02:07.300
How?

45
00:02:07.300 --> 00:02:09.800
Her phone number is on this letter.

46
00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:14.783
Yippee!

47
00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:21.500
Bonjourest il possible au speakk a Delphine

48
00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:24.800
Mummy pig is asking if Peppa
may speak to Delphine donkey.

49
00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:26.100
Hello?

50
00:02:26.100 --> 00:02:30.000
Bonjour.

51
00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.200
What do I say next?

52
00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:36.900
Comment sa va

53
00:02:36.900 --> 00:02:37.700
...byebye

54
00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:40.900
au revoir

55
00:02:40.900 --> 00:02:42.200
What did she say?

56
00:02:42.200 --> 00:02:45.400
She spoke French.

57
00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:49.500
Bonjour, George...

58
00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:52.100
Peppa is saying
"how are you" in French.

59
00:02:52.100 --> 00:02:54.600
Dinosaur...

60
00:02:54.600 --> 00:02:56.000
No, George,

61
00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.983
that's not"how are you"
speak in French.

62
00:03:02.500 --> 00:03:03.700
It is morning.

63
00:03:03.700 --> 00:03:07.100
Mr. Zebra the postman is
delivering letters to peppa's house.

64
00:03:07.100 --> 00:03:09.200
Post! Hooray!

65
00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:12.200
Can I have my letter
from Delphine, please?

66
00:03:12.200 --> 00:03:13.200
Sorry peppa,

67
00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:15.000
there is no letter for you today.

68
00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:16.800
Oh...

69
00:03:16.800 --> 00:03:20.100
I wonder who that could be.

70
00:03:20.100 --> 00:03:20.600
Bonjour.

71
00:03:20.600 --> 00:03:22.100
I am Delphine Donkey...

72
00:03:22.100 --> 00:03:24.600
I am come to see peppa.

73
00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:26.000
Its Delphine

74
00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:27.800
...Bonjour.

75
00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:29.400
Bonjour Peppa

76
00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:31.300
Here are my mama,

77
00:03:31.300 --> 00:03:35.600
pappa and brother Didia.

78
00:03:35.600 --> 00:03:39.600
Here are my mummy and daddy
and my little brother George.

79
00:03:39.600 --> 00:03:44.583
Hello... dinosaur! Dragon...

80
00:03:48.100 --> 00:03:50.500
Do you speak French, Mr. Pig?

81
00:03:50.500 --> 00:03:52.500
I am an expert at French.

82
00:03:52.500 --> 00:03:57.483
Er... yes...

83
00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:06.383
Delphine we could jump up and down
in muddy puddles.

84
00:04:06.900 --> 00:04:11.883
Delphine doesn't understand peppa.

85
00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.600
Peppa doesn't understand Delphine.

86
00:04:14.600 --> 00:04:18.500
Everything's so different
in French, daddy.

87
00:04:18.500 --> 00:04:23.483
Come on, peppa.

88
00:04:23.900 --> 00:04:28.000
J'aime sauter en haut et en
bas dans les magmas boueux

89
00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:30.400
Ah, that's what I
was going to show you.

90
00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:35.383
We call it jumping up and down
in muddy puddles.

91
00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:40.583
Everyone in the whole world loves
jumping up and down in muddy puddles.

